        <h3>Sketches</h3>
        <p>I first started with the homepage. I set out to see how I could incorporate the latest tattoos and reviews. Seeing as the bulk of the tattoo community uses Instagram for immediate display of their latest work, I thought it would be wise to highlight that feature on the homepage. It would provide a real time update without the owner having to constantly update the site with new work.</p>
